text: Kye Petersen is a pro skier, sponsored by Patagonia, Monster Energy and Oakley, Inc., who was born on January 18, 1990. Kye currently resides on the South Coast of British Columbiahttp://www.oakley.com/sports/ski/athletes/109 (2010).
